## v3.xx.x (2021-06-04)

#### :rocket: New Feature

* Now all cache structures are iterable objects
* Added new iterators `values`, `entries`
* Added `size`

#### :memo: Documentation

* Improved documentation `core/cache`

## v3.20.0 (2020-07-05)

#### :boom: Breaking Change

* Changed the returning value of `clear` from `Set` to `Map`

#### :rocket: New Feature

* Added tests
